attributes.action: Save the Cow Field in Oldfield Brow Altrincham Cheshire
attributes.additional_details: This is our only green space left in this area Lord Stamford left this for the benefit of the people who lived here,most of whom want it to stay as it is.Trafford Council want to make it a place to make money by building homes for wealthy people by the Canal.They have already got permission to build four luxury homes but have left the area devastated at Arcon Place and still not built them .Enough is enough .We want to keep this last green space
